719636f-a.title: Manhattan: Elizabeth Street - Canal Street
719636f-a.text:
28 to 2 Elizabeth Street, east side, south from Canal to Bayard
Streets, showing the rears of the former Atlantic Gardens (pitched roof,
No. 24-22) and the Thalia Theatre (adjacent). Today (1937) these have
been replaced by a 1-story business structure. See the Bowery for further
views and data.
July 26, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
